ingredient: 1/4 bunch cilantro (or green onions), roughly chopped
4 oz. frozen chopped spinach (1/4 of a 1 lb. bag)
2 cups marinara (or more to your liking)
2 15oz. cans cannellini beans, rinsed and drained
2 cups uncooked long grain jasmine rice
1 yellow onion, sliced in half moons
1/4 cup sliced Spanish olives (AKA Manzanilla olives )
